data.description: Welcome to the perfect starter or investment home, in Williams Heights of Guthrie! The living room is is adorned with wooden accent walls and windows that capture alot of natural light. The kitchen features stained cabinetry, tons of storage, builtin stove and oven, and a spacious pantry. The primary bedroom is large and features a walk in closet. Head out-back and enjoy a spacious backyard, perfect for unwinding. Don't miss your chance to call this property "Home”.
